                Silvano D<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>m</abbr><ex>estico</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Silvanae <lb n="3"/>Seius <expan><abbr>Ingen</abbr><ex>uus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> pro se <lb n="5"/>et suis <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>me</abbr><ex>rito</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Antonin</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> III <supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> Geta <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>are</ex></expan> II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z.7 befindet sich auf der crepido. (B): Fitz; Pinterović; AE 1978; Schallmayer - Eibl - Ott - Preuss - Wittkopf; Schejbal: Leseabweichungen.</p>
